OL,3,CMan jailed for three years for killing
OL,4,Cfriend in arson
OL,6,FA man found guilty of killing his
OL,7,Ffriend in a house fire has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor three-and-a-half years.
OL,10,FGary Magee, who is 44, was sentenced
OL,11,Fto a total of seven years and will
OL,12,Fspend half of the sentence on release
OL,13,Fon license.
OL,15,FJimmy Thompson, 62, died in his home
OL,16,Fin May 2021 after three deliberate
OL,17,Ffires were started in different rooms
OL,18,Fby Magee.
