OL,6,FThe judge told the court that Magee
OL,7,Facted in a 'highly reckless' manner
OL,8,Fand knew the victim, who suffered from
OL,9,Fmultiple conditions, was vulnerable.
OL,10,FMr Thompson's family members attended
OL,11,FNewry Crown Court where they remained
OL,12,Fsilent as the sentence was handed down.
